name: • Isn't The Answer •
description: It's been a long time since I've talked about some things. So I don't know how to do it or I do it badly. When I look at my life and its secret color, there is in me like a tremor of tears. Just like this sky. It is at once rain and sun, noon and midnight. Do not look backward or forward, look into yourself without fear or nostalgia. No one delves into himself as long as he remains a slave to the past or the future.
